-- San Luis Obispo County EMS Agency protocols
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'SLO-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'San Luis Obispo County cardiac arrest protocol. High-quality CPR. Defibrillation 200J. Epinephrine 1mg IV/IO q3-5min. Amiodarone 300mg first dose.', 'https://www.slocounty.ca.gov/Departments/Health-Agency/Public-Health/EMS-Agency.aspx', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'San Luis Obispo County EMS Agency' AND c.state = 'California';
